    "The study suggests students' overall sentiment towards ChatGPT, shaped by factors such as perceived usefulness and ease of use, has a significant impact on their decision to use this AI tool in their educational pursuits.",
    "There are significant theoretical and practical implications for this study.",
    "The first theoretical Implication is related to the TAM model.",
    "The positive influence of perceived usefulness and ease of use on the intention to use ChatGPT aligns with TAM and similar theoretical frameworks.",
    "This reinforces the applicability of established models in predicting technology adoption in educational contexts."
